rules.name: Suspicious Scripting in a WMI Consumer
rules.splunk: (Destination="*new-object*" Destination="*net.webclient*" Destination="*.downloadstring*") OR (Destination="*new-object*" Destination="*net.webclient*" Destination="*.downloadfile*") OR Destination IN ("* iex(*", "* -nop *", "* -noprofile *", "* -decode *", "* -enc *", "*WScript.Shell*", "*System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform*") | table User,Operation
rules.elastic: (process.executable:*new\-object* AND process.executable:*net.webclient* AND process.executable:*.downloadstring*) OR (process.executable:*new\-object* AND process.executable:*net.webclient* AND process.executable:*.downloadfile*) OR (process.executable:("*\ iex\(*" OR "*\ \-nop\ *" OR "*\ \-noprofile\ *" OR "*\ \-decode\ *" OR "*\ \-enc\ *" OR *WScript.Shell* OR *System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform*))
rules.insightidr: Destination ICONTAINS-ALL ["new-object", "net.webclient", ".downloadstring"] OR Destination ICONTAINS-ALL ["new-object", "net.webclient", ".downloadfile"] OR Destination ICONTAINS-ANY [" iex(", " -nop ", " -noprofile ", " -decode ", " -enc ", "WScript.Shell", "System.Security.Cryptography.FromBase64Transform"]

rules.name: Suspicious Encoded Scripts in a WMI Consumer
rules.splunk: Destination="*V3JpdGVQcm9jZXNzTWVtb3J5*" OR Destination="*dyaXRlUHJvY2Vzc01lbW9ye*" OR Destination="*Xcml0ZVByb2Nlc3NNZW1vcn*" OR Destination="*VGhpcyBwcm9ncmFtIGNhbm5vdCBiZSBydW4gaW4gRE9TIG1vZG*" OR Destination="*RoaXMgcHJvZ3JhbSBjYW5ub3QgYmUgcnVuIGluIERPUyBtb2Rl*" OR Destination="*UaGlzIHByb2dyYW0gY2Fubm90IGJlIHJ1biBpbiBET1MgbW9kZ*" OR Destination="*VGhpcyBwcm9ncmFtIG11c3QgYmUgcnVuIHVuZGVyIFdpbjMy*" OR Destination="*RoaXMgcHJvZ3JhbSBtdXN0IGJlIHJ1biB1bmRlciBXaW4zM*" OR Destination="*UaGlzIHByb2dyYW0gbXVzdCBiZSBydW4gdW5kZXIgV2luMz*" | table User,Operation
rules.elastic: process.executable:*V3JpdGVQcm9jZXNzTWVtb3J5* OR process.executable:*dyaXRlUHJvY2Vzc01lbW9ye* OR process.executable:*Xcml0ZVByb2Nlc3NNZW1vcn* OR process.executable:*VGhpcyBwcm9ncmFtIGNhbm5vdCBiZSBydW4gaW4gRE9TIG1vZG* OR process.executable:*RoaXMgcHJvZ3JhbSBjYW5ub3QgYmUgcnVuIGluIERPUyBtb2Rl* OR process.executable:*UaGlzIHByb2dyYW0gY2Fubm90IGJlIHJ1biBpbiBET1MgbW9kZ* OR process.executable:*VGhpcyBwcm9ncmFtIG11c3QgYmUgcnVuIHVuZGVyIFdpbjMy* OR process.executable:*RoaXMgcHJvZ3JhbSBtdXN0IGJlIHJ1biB1bmRlciBXaW4zM* OR process.executable:*UaGlzIHByb2dyYW0gbXVzdCBiZSBydW4gdW5kZXIgV2luMz*
rules.insightidr: Destination ICONTAINS "V3JpdGVQcm9jZXNzTWVtb3J5" OR Destination ICONTAINS "dyaXRlUHJvY2Vzc01lbW9ye" OR Destination ICONTAINS "Xcml0ZVByb2Nlc3NNZW1vcn" OR Destination ICONTAINS "VGhpcyBwcm9ncmFtIGNhbm5vdCBiZSBydW4gaW4gRE9TIG1vZG" OR Destination ICONTAINS "RoaXMgcHJvZ3JhbSBjYW5ub3QgYmUgcnVuIGluIERPUyBtb2Rl" OR Destination ICONTAINS "UaGlzIHByb2dyYW0gY2Fubm90IGJlIHJ1biBpbiBET1MgbW9kZ" OR Destination ICONTAINS "VGhpcyBwcm9ncmFtIG11c3QgYmUgcnVuIHVuZGVyIFdpbjMy" OR Destination ICONTAINS "RoaXMgcHJvZ3JhbSBtdXN0IGJlIHJ1biB1bmRlciBXaW4zM" OR Destination ICONTAINS "UaGlzIHByb2dyYW0gbXVzdCBiZSBydW4gdW5kZXIgV2luMz"

rules.name: WMI Event Subscription
rules.elastic: event.code:(19 OR 20 OR 21)

rules.name: Sysmon File Executable Creation Detected
rules.elastic: winlog.channel:Microsoft\-Windows\-Sysmon\/Operational AND event.code:29
rules.insightidr: EventID=29

rules.name: Sysmon Blocked File Shredding
rules.elastic: winlog.channel:Microsoft\-Windows\-Sysmon\/Operational AND event.code:28
rules.insightidr: EventID=28

rules.name: Sysmon Blocked Executable
rules.elastic: winlog.channel:Microsoft\-Windows\-Sysmon\/Operational AND event.code:27
rules.insightidr: EventID=27

rules.name: Sysmon Configuration Modification
rules.splunk: State="Stopped" OR "Sysmon config state changed" NOT State="Started"
rules.elastic: (winlog.event_data.State:Stopped OR ""Sysmon\ config\ state\ changed"") AND (NOT winlog.event_data.State:Started)
rules.insightidr: (State = NOCASE("Stopped") OR "Sysmon config state changed") AND NOT State = NOCASE("Started")

rules.name: Sysmon Configuration Error
rules.splunk: Description IN ("*Failed to open service configuration with error*", "*Failed to connect to the driver to update configuration*") NOT ((Description="*Failed to open service configuration with error*" Description="*Last error: The media is write protected.*") OR Description IN ("*Failed to open service configuration with error 19*", "*Failed to open service configuration with error 93*"))
rules.elastic: (winlog.event_data.Description:("*Failed\ to\ open\ service\ configuration\ with\ error*" OR "*Failed\ to\ connect\ to\ the\ driver\ to\ update\ configuration*")) AND (NOT ((winlog.event_data.Description:"*Failed\ to\ open\ service\ configuration\ with\ error*" AND winlog.event_data.Description:"*Last\ error\:\ The\ media\ is\ write\ protected.*") OR (winlog.event_data.Description:("*Failed\ to\ open\ service\ configuration\ with\ error\ 19*" OR "*Failed\ to\ open\ service\ configuration\ with\ error\ 93*"))))
rules.insightidr: (Description ICONTAINS-ANY ["Failed to open service configuration with error", "Failed to connect to the driver to update configuration"]) AND NOT (Description ICONTAINS-ALL ["Failed to open service configuration with error", "Last error: The media is write protected."] OR Description ICONTAINS-ANY ["Failed to open service configuration with error 19", "Failed to open service configuration with error 93"])

rules.name: Sysmon Configuration Change
rules.elastic: winlog.channel:Microsoft\-Windows\-Sysmon\/Operational AND event.code:16
rules.insightidr: EventID=16

rules.name: Winlogon Notify Key Logon Persistence
rules.elastic: registry.path:"*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon\\Notify\\logon" AND winlog.event_data.Details:*.dll
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon\\Notify\\logon$/i AND Details=/.*\.dll$/i

rules.name: Winlogon AllowMultipleTSSessions Enable
rules.elastic: registry.path:"*\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon\\AllowMultipleTSSessions" AND winlog.event_data.Details:"*DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)"
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon\\AllowMultipleTSSessions$/i AND Details=/.*DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)$/i

rules.name: Enable Local Manifest Installation With Winget
rules.elastic: registry.path:*\\AppInstaller\\EnableLocalManifestFiles AND winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)"
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*\\AppInstaller\\EnableLocalManifestFiles$/i AND Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000001)")

rules.name: Winget Admin Settings Modification
rules.elastic: process.executable:*\\winget.exe AND registry.path:\\REGISTRY\\A\\* AND registry.path:*\\LocalState\\admin_settings
rules.insightidr: Image=/.*\\winget\.exe$/i AND TargetObject ISTARTS-WITH "\REGISTRY\A\" AND TargetObject=/.*\\LocalState\\admin_settings$/i

rules.name: Disable Windows Defender Functionalities Via Registry Keys
rules.splunk: TargetObject IN ("*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows Defender\\*", "*\\SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows Defender Security Center\\*", "*\\SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows Defender\\*") (TargetObject IN ("*\\DisableAntiSpyware", "*\\DisableAntiVirus", "*\\Real-Time Protection\\DisableBehaviorMonitoring", "*\\Real-Time Protection\\DisableIntrusionPreventionSystem", "*\\Real-Time Protection\\DisableIOAVProtection", "*\\Real-Time Protection\\DisableOnAccessProtection", "*\\Real-Time Protection\\DisableRealtimeMonitoring", "*\\Real-Time Protection\\DisableScanOnRealtimeEnable", "*\\Real-Time Protection\\DisableScriptScanning", "*\\Reporting\\DisableEnhancedNotifications", "*\\SpyNet\\DisableBlockAtFirstSeen") Details="DWORD (0x00000001)") OR (TargetObject IN ("*\\App and Browser protection\\DisallowExploitProtectionOverride", "*\\Features\\TamperProtection", "*\\MpEngine\\MpEnablePus", "*\\PUAProtection", "*\\Signature Update\\ForceUpdateFromMU", "*\\SpyNet\\SpynetReporting", "*\\SpyNet\\SubmitSamplesConsent", "*\\Windows Defender Exploit Guard\\Controlled Folder Access\\EnableControlledFolderAccess") Details="DWORD (0x00000000)")
rules.elastic: (registry.path:("*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\ Defender\\*" OR "*\\SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows\ Defender\ Security\ Center\\*" OR "*\\SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows\ Defender\\*")) AND (((registry.path:(*\\DisableAntiSpyware OR *\\DisableAntiVirus OR "*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableBehaviorMonitoring" OR "*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableIntrusionPreventionSystem" OR "*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableIOAVProtection" OR "*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableOnAccessProtection" OR "*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableRealtimeMonitoring" OR "*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableScanOnRealtimeEnable" OR "*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableScriptScanning" OR *\\Reporting\\DisableEnhancedNotifications OR *\\SpyNet\\DisableBlockAtFirstSeen)) AND winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)") OR ((registry.path:("*\\App\ and\ Browser\ protection\\DisallowExploitProtectionOverride" OR *\\Features\\TamperProtection OR *\\MpEngine\\MpEnablePus OR *\\PUAProtection OR "*\\Signature\ Update\\ForceUpdateFromMU" OR *\\SpyNet\\SpynetReporting OR *\\SpyNet\\SubmitSamplesConsent OR "*\\Windows\ Defender\ Exploit\ Guard\\Controlled\ Folder\ Access\\EnableControlledFolderAccess")) AND winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000000\)"))
rules.insightidr: (TargetObject ICONTAINS-ANY ["\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows Defender\", "\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows Defender Security Center\", "\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows Defender\"]) AND ((TargetObject=/(.*\\DisableAntiSpyware$|.*\\DisableAntiVirus$|.*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableBehaviorMonitoring$|.*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableIntrusionPreventionSystem$|.*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableIOAVProtection$|.*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableOnAccessProtection$|.*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableRealtimeMonitoring$|.*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableScanOnRealtimeEnable$|.*\\Real\-Time\ Protection\\DisableScriptScanning$|.*\\Reporting\\DisableEnhancedNotifications$|.*\\SpyNet\\DisableBlockAtFirstSeen$)/i) AND Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000001)") OR (TargetObject=/(.*\\App\ and\ Browser\ protection\\DisallowExploitProtectionOverride$|.*\\Features\\TamperProtection$|.*\\MpEngine\\MpEnablePus$|.*\\PUAProtection$|.*\\Signature\ Update\\ForceUpdateFromMU$|.*\\SpyNet\\SpynetReporting$|.*\\SpyNet\\SubmitSamplesConsent$|.*\\Windows\ Defender\ Exploit\ Guard\\Controlled\ Folder\ Access\\EnableControlledFolderAccess$)/i) AND Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000000)"))

rules.name: Wdigest Enable UseLogonCredential
rules.elastic: registry.path:*WDigest\\UseLogonCredential AND winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)"
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*WDigest\\UseLogonCredential$/i AND Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000001)")

rules.name: Execution DLL of Choice Using WAB.EXE
rules.elastic: registry.path:*\\Software\\Microsoft\\WAB\\DLLPath AND (NOT winlog.event_data.Details:%CommonProgramFiles%\\System\\wab32.dll)
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*\\Software\\Microsoft\\WAB\\DLLPath$/i AND NOT Details = NOCASE("%CommonProgramFiles%\System\wab32.dll")

rules.name: VBScript Payload Stored in Registry
rules.splunk: TargetObject="*Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion*" Details IN ("*vbscript:*", "*jscript:*", "*mshtml,*", "*RunHTMLApplication*", "*Execute(*", "*CreateObject*", "*window.close*") NOT (TargetObject="*Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run*" OR (Image="*\\msiexec.exe" TargetObject="*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Installer\\UserData\\*" Details IN ("*\\Microsoft.NET\\Primary Interop Assemblies\\Microsoft.mshtml.dll*", "*<\\Microsoft.mshtml,fileVersion=*", "*_mshtml_dll_*", "*<\\Microsoft.mshtml,culture=*")))
rules.elastic: (registry.path:*Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion* AND (winlog.event_data.Details:(*vbscript\:* OR *jscript\:* OR *mshtml,* OR *RunHTMLApplication* OR *Execute\(* OR *CreateObject* OR *window.close*))) AND (NOT (registry.path:*Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run* OR (process.executable:*\\msiexec.exe AND registry.path:*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Installer\\UserData\\* AND (winlog.event_data.Details:("*\\Microsoft.NET\\Primary\ Interop\ Assemblies\\Microsoft.mshtml.dll*" OR *\<\\Microsoft.mshtml,fileVersion\=* OR *_mshtml_dll_* OR *\<\\Microsoft.mshtml,culture\=*)))))
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ICONTAINS "Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion" AND (Details ICONTAINS-ANY ["vbscript:", "jscript:", "mshtml,", "RunHTMLApplication", "Execute(", "CreateObject", "window.close"]) AND NOT (TargetObject ICONTAINS "Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run" OR Image=/.*\\msiexec\.exe$/i AND TargetObject ICONTAINS "\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Installer\UserData\" AND (Details ICONTAINS-ANY ["\Microsoft.NET\Primary Interop Assemblies\Microsoft.mshtml.dll", "<\Microsoft.mshtml,fileVersion=", "_mshtml_dll_", "<\Microsoft.mshtml,culture="]))

rules.name: UAC Bypass Using Windows Media Player - Registry
rules.splunk: TargetObject="*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\AppCompatFlags\\Compatibility Assistant\\Store\\C:\\Program Files\\Windows Media Player\\osk.exe" Details="Binary Data"
rules.elastic: registry.path:"*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\AppCompatFlags\\Compatibility\ Assistant\\Store\\C\:\\Program\ Files\\Windows\ Media\ Player\\osk.exe" AND winlog.event_data.Details:"Binary\ Data"
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\AppCompatFlags\\Compatibility\ Assistant\\Store\\C:\\Program\ Files\\Windows\ Media\ Player\\osk\.exe$/i AND Details = NOCASE("Binary Data")

rules.name: UAC Bypass Abusing Winsat Path Parsing - Registry
rules.elastic: registry.path:*\\Root\\InventoryApplicationFile\\winsat.exe\|* AND registry.path:*\\LowerCaseLongPath AND winlog.event_data.Details:c\:\\users\\* AND winlog.event_data.Details:*\\appdata\\local\\temp\\system32\\winsat.exe
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ICONTAINS "\Root\InventoryApplicationFile\winsat.exe|" AND TargetObject=/.*\\LowerCaseLongPath$/i AND Details ISTARTS-WITH "c:\users\" AND Details=/.*\\appdata\\local\\temp\\system32\\winsat\.exe$/i

rules.name: UAC Bypass via Event Viewer
rules.elastic: registry.path:*\\mscfile\\shell\\open\\command
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*\\mscfile\\shell\\open\\command$/i

rules.name: Potential Signing Bypass Via Windows Developer Features - Registry
rules.elastic: (registry.path:(*\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\AppModelUnlock* OR *\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Appx\\*)) AND (registry.path:(*\\AllowAllTrustedApps OR *\\AllowDevelopmentWithoutDevLicense)) AND winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)"
rules.insightidr: (TargetObject ICONTAINS-ANY ["\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\AppModelUnlock", "\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\Appx\"]) AND (TargetObject=/(.*\\AllowAllTrustedApps$|.*\\AllowDevelopmentWithoutDevLicense$)/i) AND Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000001)")

rules.name: COM Hijacking via TreatAs
rules.splunk: TargetObject="*TreatAs\\(Default)" NOT ((Image="C:\\Program Files\\Common Files\\Microsoft Shared\\ClickToRun\\*" Image="*\\OfficeClickToRun.exe") OR Image="C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft Office\\root\\integration\\integrator.exe" OR Image="C:\\Windows\\system32\\svchost.exe" OR Image IN ("C:\\Windows\\system32\\msiexec.exe", "C:\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\msiexec.exe"))
rules.elastic: registry.path:*TreatAs\\\(Default\) AND (NOT ((process.executable:"C\:\\Program\ Files\\Common\ Files\\Microsoft\ Shared\\ClickToRun\\*" AND process.executable:*\\OfficeClickToRun.exe) OR process.executable:"C\:\\Program\ Files\ \(x86\)\\Microsoft\ Office\\root\\integration\\integrator.exe" OR process.executable:C\:\\Windows\\system32\\svchost.exe OR (process.executable:(C\:\\Windows\\system32\\msiexec.exe OR C\:\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\msiexec.exe))))
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*TreatAs\\\(Default\)$/i AND NOT (Image ICONTAINS-ALL ["C:\Program Files\Common Files\Microsoft Shared\ClickToRun\", "\OfficeClickToRun.exe"] OR Image = NOCASE("C:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Office\root\integration\integrator.exe") OR Image = NOCASE("C:\Windows\system32\svchost.exe") OR Image IIN ["C:\Windows\system32\msiexec.exe", "C:\Windows\SysWOW64\msiexec.exe"])

rules.name: Old TLS1.0/TLS1.1 Protocol Version Enabled
rules.elastic: (registry.path:("*\\Control\\SecurityProviders\\SCHANNEL\\Protocols\\TLS\ 1.0\\*" OR "*\\Control\\SecurityProviders\\SCHANNEL\\Protocols\\TLS\ 1.1\\*")) AND registry.path:*\\Enabled AND winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)"
rules.insightidr: (TargetObject ICONTAINS-ANY ["\Control\SecurityProviders\SCHANNEL\Protocols\TLS 1.0\", "\Control\SecurityProviders\SCHANNEL\Protocols\TLS 1.1\"]) AND TargetObject=/.*\\Enabled$/i AND Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000001)")

rules.name: Set TimeProviders DllName
rules.elastic: (registry.path:HKLM\\System\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\W32Time\\TimeProviders* AND registry.path:*DllName) AND (NOT winlog.event_data.Details:C\:\\Windows\\SYSTEM32\\w32time.DLL)
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ICONTAINS-ALL ["HKLM\System\CurrentControlSet\Services\W32Time\TimeProviders", "DllName"] AND NOT Details = NOCASE("C:\Windows\SYSTEM32\w32time.DLL")

rules.name: RDP Sensitive Settings Changed
rules.splunk: (TargetObject IN ("*SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\Terminal Services\\*", "*\\Control\\Terminal Server\\*") TargetObject="*\\Shadow" Details IN ("DWORD (0x00000001)", "DWORD (0x00000002)", "DWORD (0x00000003)", "DWORD (0x00000004)")) OR (TargetObject IN ("*\\Control\\Terminal Server\\*", "*SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\Terminal Services\\*") TargetObject IN ("*\\fAllowUnsolicited", "*\\fAllowUnsolicitedFullControl") Details="DWORD (0x00000001)") OR TargetObject IN ("*\\services\\TermService\\Parameters\\ServiceDll*", "*\\Control\\Terminal Server\\WinStations\\RDP-Tcp\\InitialProgram*", "*\\Control\\Terminal Server\\InitialProgram*", "*SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\Terminal Services\\InitialProgram*")
rules.elastic: ((registry.path:("*SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\Terminal\ Services\\*" OR "*\\Control\\Terminal\ Server\\*")) AND registry.path:*\\Shadow AND (winlog.event_data.Details:("DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)" OR "DWORD\ \(0x00000002\)" OR "DWORD\ \(0x00000003\)" OR "DWORD\ \(0x00000004\)"))) OR ((registry.path:("*\\Control\\Terminal\ Server\\*" OR "*SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\Terminal\ Services\\*")) AND ((registry.path:(*\\fAllowUnsolicited OR *\\fAllowUnsolicitedFullControl)) AND winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)")) OR (registry.path:(*\\services\\TermService\\Parameters\\ServiceDll* OR "*\\Control\\Terminal\ Server\\WinStations\\RDP\-Tcp\\InitialProgram*" OR "*\\Control\\Terminal\ Server\\InitialProgram*" OR "*SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\Terminal\ Services\\InitialProgram*"))
rules.insightidr: (TargetObject ICONTAINS-ANY ["SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows NT\Terminal Services\", "\Control\Terminal Server\"]) AND TargetObject=/.*\\Shadow$/i AND (Details IIN ["DWORD (0x00000001)", "DWORD (0x00000002)", "DWORD (0x00000003)", "DWORD (0x00000004)"]) OR (TargetObject ICONTAINS-ANY ["\Control\Terminal Server\", "SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows NT\Terminal Services\"]) AND (TargetObject=/(.*\\fAllowUnsolicited$|.*\\fAllowUnsolicitedFullControl$)/i) AND Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000001)") OR TargetObject ICONTAINS-ANY ["\services\TermService\Parameters\ServiceDll", "\Control\Terminal Server\WinStations\RDP-Tcp\InitialProgram", "\Control\Terminal Server\InitialProgram", "SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows NT\Terminal Services\InitialProgram"]

rules.name: RDP Sensitive Settings Changed to Zero
rules.elastic: (registry.path:(*\\fDenyTSConnections OR *\\fSingleSessionPerUser OR *\\UserAuthentication)) AND winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000000\)"
rules.insightidr: (TargetObject=/(.*\\fDenyTSConnections$|.*\\fSingleSessionPerUser$|.*\\UserAuthentication$)/i) AND Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000000)")

rules.name: Potential Registry Persistence Attempt Via Windows Telemetry
rules.elastic: (registry.path:"*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\AppCompatFlags\\TelemetryController\\*" AND registry.path:*\\Command AND (winlog.event_data.Details:(*.bat* OR *.bin* OR *.cmd* OR *.dat* OR *.dll* OR *.exe* OR *.hta* OR *.jar* OR *.js* OR *.msi* OR *.ps* OR *.sh* OR *.vb*))) AND (NOT (winlog.event_data.Details:(*\\system32\\CompatTelRunner.exe* OR *\\system32\\DeviceCensus.exe*)))
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ICONTAINS "\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\AppCompatFlags\TelemetryController\" AND TargetObject=/.*\\Command$/i AND (Details ICONTAINS-ANY [".bat", ".bin", ".cmd", ".dat", ".dll", ".exe", ".hta", ".jar", ".js", ".msi", ".ps", ".sh", ".vb"]) AND NOT (Details ICONTAINS-ANY ["\system32\CompatTelRunner.exe", "\system32\DeviceCensus.exe"])

rules.name: Scheduled TaskCache Change by Uncommon Program
rules.splunk: TargetObject="*SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Schedule\\TaskCache\\*" NOT (TargetObject IN ("*Microsoft\\Windows\\UpdateOrchestrator*", "*Microsoft\\Windows\\SoftwareProtectionPlatform\\SvcRestartTask\\Index*", "*Microsoft\\Windows\\Flighting\\OneSettings\\RefreshCache\\Index*") OR (Image="C:\\Windows\\*" Image="*\\TiWorker.exe") OR Image="C:\\WINDOWS\\system32\\svchost.exe" OR (Image="C:\\Windows\\Microsoft.NET\\Framework*" Image="*\\ngen.exe" TargetObject IN ("*\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Schedule\\TaskCache\\Tasks\\{B66B135D-DA06-4FC4-95F8-7458E1D10129}*", "*\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Schedule\\TaskCache\\Tree\\Microsoft\\Windows\\.NET Framework\\.NET Framework NGEN*")) OR Image IN ("C:\\Program Files\\Microsoft Office\\root\\Integration\\Integrator.exe", "C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft Office\\root\\Integration\\Integrator.exe") OR Image="C:\\Windows\\System32\\msiexec.exe" OR Image IN ("C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Dropbox\\Update\\DropboxUpdate.exe", "C:\\Program Files\\Dropbox\\Update\\DropboxUpdate.exe") OR (Image="C:\\Windows\\explorer.exe" TargetObject="*\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Schedule\\TaskCache\\Tree\\Microsoft\\Windows\\PLA\\Server Manager Performance Monitor\\*") OR Image="System")
rules.elastic: registry.path:"*SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\Schedule\\TaskCache\\*" AND (NOT ((registry.path:(*Microsoft\\Windows\\UpdateOrchestrator* OR *Microsoft\\Windows\\SoftwareProtectionPlatform\\SvcRestartTask\\Index* OR *Microsoft\\Windows\\Flighting\\OneSettings\\RefreshCache\\Index*)) OR (process.executable:C\:\\Windows\\* AND process.executable:*\\TiWorker.exe) OR process.executable:C\:\\WINDOWS\\system32\\svchost.exe OR (process.executable:C\:\\Windows\\Microsoft.NET\\Framework* AND process.executable:*\\ngen.exe AND (registry.path:("*\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\Schedule\\TaskCache\\Tasks\\\{B66B135D\-DA06\-4FC4\-95F8\-7458E1D10129\}*" OR "*\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\Schedule\\TaskCache\\Tree\\Microsoft\\Windows\\.NET\ Framework\\.NET\ Framework\ NGEN*"))) OR (process.executable:("C\:\\Program\ Files\\Microsoft\ Office\\root\\Integration\\Integrator.exe" OR "C\:\\Program\ Files\ \(x86\)\\Microsoft\ Office\\root\\Integration\\Integrator.exe")) OR process.executable:C\:\\Windows\\System32\\msiexec.exe OR (process.executable:("C\:\\Program\ Files\ \(x86\)\\Dropbox\\Update\\DropboxUpdate.exe" OR "C\:\\Program\ Files\\Dropbox\\Update\\DropboxUpdate.exe")) OR (process.executable:C\:\\Windows\\explorer.exe AND registry.path:"*\\Microsoft\\Windows\ NT\\CurrentVersion\\Schedule\\TaskCache\\Tree\\Microsoft\\Windows\\PLA\\Server\ Manager\ Performance\ Monitor\\*") OR process.executable:System))

rules.name: CrashControl CrashDump Disabled
rules.elastic: registry.path:*SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\CrashControl* AND winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000000\)"
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ICONTAINS "SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\CrashControl" AND Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000000)")

rules.name: COM Hijack via Sdclt
rules.elastic: registry.path:*\\Software\\Classes\\Folder\\shell\\open\\command\\DelegateExecute*
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ICONTAINS "\Software\Classes\Folder\shell\open\command\DelegateExecute"

rules.name: CobaltStrike Service Installations in Registry
rules.elastic: registry.path:*HKLM\\System\\CurrentControlSet\\Services* AND ((winlog.event_data.Details:*ADMIN$* AND winlog.event_data.Details:*.exe*) OR (winlog.event_data.Details:*%COMSPEC%* AND winlog.event_data.Details:*start* AND winlog.event_data.Details:*powershell*))
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ICONTAINS "HKLM\System\CurrentControlSet\Services" AND (Details ICONTAINS-ALL ["ADMIN$", ".exe"] OR Details ICONTAINS-ALL ["%COMSPEC%", "start", "powershell"])

rules.name: ClickOnce Trust Prompt Tampering
rules.elastic: registry.path:*\\SOFTWARE\\MICROSOFT\\.NETFramework\\Security\\TrustManager\\PromptingLevel\\* AND (registry.path:(*\\Internet OR *\\LocalIntranet OR *\\MyComputer OR *\\TrustedSites OR *\\UntrustedSites)) AND winlog.event_data.Details:Enabled
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ICONTAINS "\SOFTWARE\MICROSOFT\.NETFramework\Security\TrustManager\PromptingLevel\" AND (TargetObject=/(.*\\Internet$|.*\\LocalIntranet$|.*\\MyComputer$|.*\\TrustedSites$|.*\\UntrustedSites$)/i) AND Details = NOCASE("Enabled")

rules.name: Change Winevt Event Access Permission Via Registry
rules.elastic: (registry.path:HKLM\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\WINEVT\\Channels\\* AND registry.path:*\\ChannelAccess AND (winlog.event_data.Details:(*\(A;;0x1;;;SY\)* OR *\(A;;0x5;;;BA\)* OR *\(A;;0x1;;;LA\)*))) AND (NOT (process.executable:(C\:\\Windows\\servicing\\TrustedInstaller.exe OR *\\TiWorker.exe)))
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ISTARTS-WITH "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\WINEVT\Channels\" AND TargetObject=/.*\\ChannelAccess$/i AND (Details ICONTAINS-ANY ["(A;;0x1;;;SY)", "(A;;0x5;;;BA)", "(A;;0x1;;;LA)"]) AND NOT (Image IIN ["C:\Windows\servicing\TrustedInstaller.exe", "\TiWorker.exe"])

rules.name: Disable Sysmon Event Logging Via Registry
rules.elastic: registry.path:HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\* AND registry.path:"*\\Instances\\Sysmon\ Instance\\Altitude"
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ICONTAINS-ALL ["HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\", "\Instances\Sysmon Instance\Altitude"]

rules.name: IE Change Domain Zone
rules.elastic: registry.path:"*\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Internet\ Settings\\ZoneMap\\Domains\\*" AND (NOT (winlog.event_data.Details:("DWORD\ \(0x00000000\)" OR "DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)" OR \(Empty\))))
rules.insightidr: TargetObject ICONTAINS "\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Internet Settings\ZoneMap\Domains\" AND NOT (Details IIN ["DWORD (0x00000000)", "DWORD (0x00000001)", "(Empty)"])

rules.name: Changing RDP Port to Non Standard Number
rules.elastic: registry.path:"HKLM\\System\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Terminal\ Server\\WinStations\\RDP\-Tcp\\PortNumber" AND (NOT winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000d3d\)")
rules.insightidr: TargetObject = NOCASE("HKLM\System\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server\WinStations\RDP-Tcp\PortNumber") AND NOT Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000d3d)")

rules.name: Bypass UAC Using SilentCleanup Task
rules.elastic: registry.path:*\\Environment\\windir AND winlog.event_data.Details:*\&REM*
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*\\Environment\\windir$/i AND Details ICONTAINS "&REM"

rules.name: Bypass UAC Using Event Viewer
rules.elastic: registry.path:*_Classes\\mscfile\\shell\\open\\command\\\(Default\) AND (NOT winlog.event_data.Details:"%SystemRoot%\\system32\\mmc.exe\ \"%1\"\ %*")
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*_Classes\\mscfile\\shell\\open\\command\\\(Default\)$/i AND NOT Details ISTARTS-WITH '%SystemRoot%\system32\mmc.exe "%1" %'

rules.name: Bypass UAC Using DelegateExecute
rules.elastic: registry.path:*\\open\\command\\DelegateExecute AND winlog.event_data.Details:\(Empty\)
rules.insightidr: TargetObject=/.*\\open\\command\\DelegateExecute$/i AND Details = NOCASE("(Empty)")

rules.name: Blackbyte Ransomware Registry
rules.elastic: (registry.path:(HKLM\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Policies\\System\\LocalAccountTokenFilterPolicy OR HKLM\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Policies\\System\\EnableLinkedConnections OR HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\FileSystem\\LongPathsEnabled)) AND winlog.event_data.Details:"DWORD\ \(0x00000001\)"
rules.insightidr: (TargetObject IIN ["HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Policies\System\LocalAccountTokenFilterPolicy", "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Policies\System\EnableLinkedConnections", "HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\FileSystem\LongPathsEnabled"]) AND Details = NOCASE("DWORD (0x00000001)")

rules.name: New BgInfo.EXE Custom WMI Query Registry Configuration
rules.elastic: winlog.event_data.EventType:SetValue AND registry.path:*\\Software\\Winternals\\BGInfo\\UserFields\\* AND winlog.event_data.Details:6*
rules.insightidr: EventType = NOCASE("SetValue") AND TargetObject ICONTAINS "\Software\Winternals\BGInfo\UserFields\" AND Details ISTARTS-WITH "6"

rules.name: New BgInfo.EXE Custom VBScript Registry Configuration
rules.elastic: winlog.event_data.EventType:SetValue AND registry.path:*\\Software\\Winternals\\BGInfo\\UserFields\\* AND winlog.event_data.Details:4*
rules.insightidr: EventType = NOCASE("SetValue") AND TargetObject ICONTAINS "\Software\Winternals\BGInfo\UserFields\" AND Details ISTARTS-WITH "4"

rules.name: New BgInfo.EXE Custom DB Path Registry Configuration
rules.elastic: winlog.event_data.EventType:SetValue AND registry.path:*\\Software\\Winternals\\BGInfo\\Database
rules.insightidr: EventType = NOCASE("SetValue") AND TargetObject=/.*\\Software\\Winternals\\BGInfo\\Database$/i

rules.insightidr: (Image=/.*\\cmstp\.exe$/i OR OriginalFileName = NOCASE("CMSTP.EXE")) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["/s", "-s", "/au", "-au", "/ni", "-ni"])

rules.name: UAC Bypass Using Disk Cleanup

rules.name: Potential RDP Session Hijacking Activity

rules.insightidr: (Image=/.*\\tscon\.exe$/i OR OriginalFileName = NOCASE("tscon.exe")) AND IntegrityLevel = NOCASE("SYSTEM")

rules.insightidr: CommandLine ICONTAINS " /dest:rdp-tcp#"

rules.name: Suspicious TSCON Start as SYSTEM

rules.name: New Virtual Smart Card Created Via TpmVscMgr.EXE

rules.name: Taskmgr as Parent

rules.name: Taskmgr as LOCAL_SYSTEM

rules.insightidr: (User ICONTAINS-ANY ["AUTHORI", "AUTORI"]) AND Image=/.*\\taskmgr\.exe$/i

rules.name: Suspicious Tasklist Discovery Command
rules.elastic: process.command_line:*tasklist* OR process.executable:*\\tasklist.exe OR process.pe.original_file_name:tasklist.exe
rules.insightidr: CommandLine ICONTAINS "tasklist" OR Image=/.*\\tasklist\.exe$/i OR OriginalFileName = NOCASE("tasklist.exe")

rules.elastic: (process.command_line:(*\~1\\* OR *\~2\\*)) AND (NOT ((process.parent.executable:(C\:\\Windows\\System32\\Dism.exe OR C\:\\Windows\\System32\\cleanmgr.exe OR "C\:\\Program\ Files\\GPSoftware\\Directory\ Opus\\dopus.exe")) OR (process.parent.executable:(*\\WebEx\\WebexHost.exe OR *\\thor\\thor64.exe OR *\\veam.backup.shell.exe OR *\\winget.exe OR *\\Everything\\Everything.exe)) OR process.parent.executable:*\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\WinGet\\* OR (process.command_line:(*\\appdata\\local\\webex\\webex64\\meetings\\wbxreport.exe* OR "*C\:\\Program\ Files\\Git\\post\-install.bat*" OR "*C\:\\Program\ Files\\Git\\cmd\\scalar.exe*"))))
rules.insightidr: (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["~1\", "~2\"]) AND NOT (ParentImage IIN ["C:\Windows\System32\Dism.exe", "C:\Windows\System32\cleanmgr.exe", "C:\Program Files\GPSoftware\Directory Opus\dopus.exe"] OR ParentImage=/(.*\\WebEx\\WebexHost\.exe$|.*\\thor\\thor64\.exe$|.*\\veam\.backup\.shell\.exe$|.*\\winget\.exe$|.*\\Everything\\Everything\.exe$)/i OR ParentImage ICONTAINS "\AppData\Local\Temp\WinGet\" OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["\appdata\local\webex\webex64\meetings\wbxreport.exe", "C:\Program Files\Git\post-install.bat", "C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\scalar.exe"])

rules.name: Potentially Suspicious Call To Win32_NTEventlogFile Class

rules.elastic: (((process.executable:(*\\NTDSDump.exe OR *\\NTDSDumpEx.exe)) OR (process.command_line:*ntds.dit* AND process.command_line:*system.hiv*) OR process.command_line:*NTDSgrab.ps1*) OR (process.command_line:"*ac\ i\ ntds*" AND process.command_line:"*create\ full*") OR (process.command_line:"*\/c\ copy\ *" AND process.command_line:*\\windows\\ntds\\ntds.dit*) OR (process.command_line:"*activate\ instance\ ntds*" AND process.command_line:"*create\ full*") OR (process.command_line:*powershell* AND process.command_line:*ntds.dit*)) OR (process.command_line:*ntds.dit* AND ((process.parent.executable:(*\\apache* OR *\\tomcat* OR *\\AppData\\* OR *\\Temp\\* OR *\\Public\\* OR *\\PerfLogs\\*)) OR (process.executable:(*\\apache* OR *\\tomcat* OR *\\AppData\\* OR *\\Temp\\* OR *\\Public\\* OR *\\PerfLogs\\*))))
rules.insightidr: Image=/(.*\\NTDSDump\.exe$|.*\\NTDSDumpEx\.exe$)/i OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["ntds.dit", "system.hiv"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS "NTDSgrab.ps1" OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["ac i ntds", "create full"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["/c copy ", "\windows\ntds\ntds.dit"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["activate instance ntds", "create full"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["powershell", "ntds.dit"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS "ntds.dit" AND (ParentImage ICONTAINS-ANY ["\apache", "\tomcat", "\AppData\", "\Temp\", "\Public\", "\PerfLogs\"] OR Image ICONTAINS-ANY ["\apache", "\tomcat", "\AppData\", "\Temp\", "\Public\", "\PerfLogs\"])

rules.name: Non-privileged Usage of Reg or Powershell
rules.splunk: (CommandLine="*reg *" CommandLine="*add*") OR CommandLine IN ("*powershell*", "*set-itemproperty*", "* sp *", "*new-itemproperty*") IntegrityLevel="Medium" CommandLine="*ControlSet*" CommandLine="*Services*" CommandLine IN ("*ImagePath*", "*FailureCommand*", "*ServiceDLL*") | table EventCode,IntegrityLevel,CommandLine
rules.elastic: ((process.command_line:"*reg\ *" AND process.command_line:*add*) OR (process.command_line:(*powershell* OR *set\-itemproperty* OR "*\ sp\ *" OR *new\-itemproperty*))) AND (winlog.event_data.IntegrityLevel:Medium AND (process.command_line:*ControlSet* AND process.command_line:*Services*) AND (process.command_line:(*ImagePath* OR *FailureCommand* OR *ServiceDLL*)))
rules.insightidr: (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["reg ", "add"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["powershell", "set-itemproperty", " sp ", "new-itemproperty"]) AND IntegrityLevel = NOCASE("Medium") AND CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["ControlSet", "Services"] AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["ImagePath", "FailureCommand", "ServiceDLL"])

rules.name: Potential Network Sniffing Activity Using Network Tools
rules.elastic: (process.executable:*\\tshark.exe AND process.command_line:*\-i*) OR process.executable:*\\windump.exe
rules.insightidr: Image=/.*\\tshark\.exe$/i AND CommandLine ICONTAINS "-i" OR Image=/.*\\windump\.exe$/i

rules.name: Suspicious Scan Loop Network
rules.elastic: (process.command_line:("*for\ *" OR "*foreach\ *")) AND (process.command_line:(*nslookup* OR *ping*))
rules.insightidr: (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["for ", "foreach "]) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["nslookup", "ping"])

rules.name: Suspicious Network Command
rules.splunk: CommandLine IN ("*ipconfig /all*", "*netsh interface show interface*", "*arp -a*", "*nbtstat -n*", "*net config*", "*route print*")
rules.elastic: process.command_line:("*ipconfig\ \/all*" OR "*netsh\ interface\ show\ interface*" OR "*arp\ \-a*" OR "*nbtstat\ \-n*" OR "*net\ config*" OR "*route\ print*")
rules.insightidr: CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["ipconfig /all", "netsh interface show interface", "arp -a", "nbtstat -n", "net config", "route print"]

rules.name: Potential File Download Via MS-AppInstaller Protocol Handler
rules.elastic: process.command_line:*ms\-appinstaller\:\/\/?source\=* AND process.command_line:*http*
rules.insightidr: CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["ms-appinstaller://?source=", "http"]

rules.name: LSASS Dump Keyword In CommandLine
rules.splunk: CommandLine IN ("*lsass.dmp*", "*lsass.zip*", "*lsass.rar*", "*Andrew.dmp*", "*Coredump.dmp*", "*NotLSASS.zip*", "*lsass_2*", "*lsassdump*", "*lsassdmp*") OR (CommandLine="*lsass*" CommandLine="*.dmp*") OR (CommandLine="*SQLDmpr*" CommandLine="*.mdmp*") OR (CommandLine="*nanodump*" CommandLine="*.dmp*")
rules.elastic: (process.command_line:(*lsass.dmp* OR *lsass.zip* OR *lsass.rar* OR *Andrew.dmp* OR *Coredump.dmp* OR *NotLSASS.zip* OR *lsass_2* OR *lsassdump* OR *lsassdmp*)) OR (process.command_line:*lsass* AND process.command_line:*.dmp*) OR (process.command_line:*SQLDmpr* AND process.command_line:*.mdmp*) OR (process.command_line:*nanodump* AND process.command_line:*.dmp*)

rules.elastic: ((process.executable:(*\\calc.exe OR *\\certutil.exe OR *\\cmstp.exe OR *\\cscript.exe OR *\\installutil.exe OR *\\mshta.exe OR *\\regsvr32.exe OR *\\rundll32.exe OR *\\wscript.exe)) OR (process.pe.original_file_name:(CALC.EXE OR CertUtil.exe OR CMSTP.EXE OR cscript.exe OR installutil.exe OR MSHTA.EXE OR REGSVR32.EXE OR RUNDLL32.EXE OR wscript.exe))) AND (NOT (process.working_directory:*C\:\\* OR process.working_directory:"" OR (NOT _exists_:process.working_directory)))
rules.insightidr: (Image=/(.*\\calc\.exe$|.*\\certutil\.exe$|.*\\cmstp\.exe$|.*\\cscript\.exe$|.*\\installutil\.exe$|.*\\mshta\.exe$|.*\\regsvr32\.exe$|.*\\rundll32\.exe$|.*\\wscript\.exe$)/i OR OriginalFileName IIN ["CALC.EXE", "CertUtil.exe", "CMSTP.EXE", "cscript.exe", "installutil.exe", "MSHTA.EXE", "REGSVR32.EXE", "RUNDLL32.EXE", "wscript.exe"]) AND NOT (CurrentDirectory ICONTAINS "C:\" OR CurrentDirectory = NOCASE("") OR CurrentDirectory = null)

rules.name: Local Accounts Discovery
rules.splunk: (Image="*\\cmd.exe" CommandLine="* /c*" CommandLine="*dir *" CommandLine="*\\Users\\*" NOT CommandLine="* rmdir *") OR (Image IN ("*\\net.exe", "*\\net1.exe") CommandLine="*user*" NOT (CommandLine IN ("*/domain*", "*/add*", "*/delete*", "*/active*", "*/expires*", "*/passwordreq*", "*/scriptpath*", "*/times*", "*/workstations*"))) OR Image IN ("*\\whoami.exe", "*\\quser.exe", "*\\qwinsta.exe") OR (Image="*\\wmic.exe" CommandLine="*useraccount*" CommandLine="*get*") OR (Image="*\\cmdkey.exe" CommandLine="* /l*")
rules.elastic: ((process.executable:*\\cmd.exe AND (process.command_line:"*\ \/c*" AND process.command_line:"*dir\ *" AND process.command_line:*\\Users\\*)) AND (NOT process.command_line:"*\ rmdir\ *")) OR (((process.executable:(*\\net.exe OR *\\net1.exe)) AND process.command_line:*user*) AND (NOT (process.command_line:(*\/domain* OR *\/add* OR *\/delete* OR *\/active* OR *\/expires* OR *\/passwordreq* OR *\/scriptpath* OR *\/times* OR *\/workstations*)))) OR ((process.executable:(*\\whoami.exe OR *\\quser.exe OR *\\qwinsta.exe)) OR (process.executable:*\\wmic.exe AND (process.command_line:*useraccount* AND process.command_line:*get*)) OR (process.executable:*\\cmdkey.exe AND process.command_line:"*\ \/l*"))

rules.elastic: (process.executable:*\\regsvr32.exe OR process.pe.original_file_name:REGSVR32.EXE) AND ((process.command_line:(*\:\\PerfLogs\\* OR *\:\\Temp\\* OR *\\Windows\\Registration\\CRMLog* OR *\\Windows\\System32\\com\\dmp\\* OR *\\Windows\\System32\\FxsTmp\\* OR *\\Windows\\System32\\Microsoft\\Crypto\\RSA\\MachineKeys\\* OR *\\Windows\\System32\\spool\\drivers\\color\\* OR *\\Windows\\System32\\spool\\PRINTERS\\* OR *\\Windows\\System32\\spool\\SERVERS\\* OR *\\Windows\\System32\\Tasks_Migrated\\* OR *\\Windows\\System32\\Tasks\\Microsoft\\Windows\\SyncCenter\\* OR *\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\com\\dmp\\* OR *\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\FxsTmp\\* OR *\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\Tasks\\Microsoft\\Windows\\PLA\\System\\* OR *\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\Tasks\\Microsoft\\Windows\\SyncCenter\\* OR *\\Windows\\Tasks\\* OR *\\Windows\\Tracing\\*)) OR ((process.command_line:("*\ \"C\:\\*" OR "*\ C\:\\*" OR "*\ 'C\:\\*" OR *D\:\\*)) AND (NOT (process.command_line:("*C\:\\Program\ Files\ \(x86\)\\*" OR "*C\:\\Program\ Files\\*" OR *C\:\\ProgramData\\* OR *C\:\\Users\\* OR "*\ C\:\\Windows\\*" OR "*\ \"C\:\\Windows\\*" OR "*\ 'C\:\\Windows\\*"))))) AND (NOT (process.command_line:"" OR (NOT _exists_:process.command_line)))
rules.insightidr: (Image=/.*\\regsvr32\.exe$/i OR OriginalFileName = NOCASE("REGSVR32.EXE")) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [":\PerfLogs\", ":\Temp\", "\Windows\Registration\CRMLog", "\Windows\System32\com\dmp\", "\Windows\System32\FxsTmp\", "\Windows\System32\Microsoft\Crypto\RSA\MachineKeys\", "\Windows\System32\spool\drivers\color\", "\Windows\System32\spool\PRINTERS\", "\Windows\System32\spool\SERVERS\", "\Windows\System32\Tasks_Migrated\", "\Windows\System32\Tasks\Microsoft\Windows\SyncCenter\", "\Windows\SysWOW64\com\dmp\", "\Windows\SysWOW64\FxsTmp\", "\Windows\SysWOW64\Tasks\Microsoft\Windows\PLA\System\", "\Windows\SysWOW64\Tasks\Microsoft\Windows\SyncCenter\", "\Windows\Tasks\", "\Windows\Tracing\"] OR (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [' "C:\', " C:\", """ 'C:\""", "D:\"]) AND NOT (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["C:\Program Files (x86)\", "C:\Program Files\", "C:\ProgramData\", "C:\Users\", " C:\Windows\", ' "C:\Windows\', """ 'C:\Windows\"""])) AND NOT (CommandLine = NOCASE("") OR CommandLine = null)

rules.name: Regsvr32 Execution From Potential Suspicious Location
rules.elastic: (process.executable:*\\regsvr32.exe OR process.pe.original_file_name:REGSVR32.EXE) AND (process.command_line:(*\:\\ProgramData\\* OR *\:\\Temp\\* OR *\:\\Users\\Public\\* OR *\:\\Windows\\Temp\\* OR *\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\* OR *\\AppData\\Roaming\\*))
rules.insightidr: (Image=/.*\\regsvr32\.exe$/i OR OriginalFileName = NOCASE("REGSVR32.EXE")) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [":\ProgramData\", ":\Temp\", ":\Users\Public\", ":\Windows\Temp\", "\AppData\Local\Temp\", "\AppData\Roaming\"])

rules.name: Potentially Suspicious Child Process Of Regsvr32
rules.elastic: (process.parent.executable:*\\regsvr32.exe AND (process.executable:(*\\calc.exe OR *\\cscript.exe OR *\\explorer.exe OR *\\mshta.exe OR *\\net.exe OR *\\net1.exe OR *\\nltest.exe OR *\\notepad.exe OR *\\powershell.exe OR *\\pwsh.exe OR *\\reg.exe OR *\\schtasks.exe OR *\\werfault.exe OR *\\wscript.exe))) AND (NOT (process.executable:*\\werfault.exe AND process.command_line:"*\ \-u\ \-p\ *"))
rules.insightidr: ParentImage=/.*\\regsvr32\.exe$/i AND (Image=/(.*\\calc\.exe$|.*\\cscript\.exe$|.*\\explorer\.exe$|.*\\mshta\.exe$|.*\\net\.exe$|.*\\net1\.exe$|.*\\nltest\.exe$|.*\\notepad\.exe$|.*\\powershell\.exe$|.*\\pwsh\.exe$|.*\\reg\.exe$|.*\\schtasks\.exe$|.*\\werfault\.exe$|.*\\wscript\.exe$)/i) AND NOT (Image=/.*\\werfault\.exe$/i AND CommandLine ICONTAINS " -u -p ")

rules.name: Suspicious Regsvr32 Execution From Remote Share
rules.elastic: (process.executable:*\\regsvr32.exe OR process.pe.original_file_name:\\REGSVR32.EXE) AND process.command_line:"*\ \\\\*"
rules.insightidr: (Image=/.*\\regsvr32\.exe$/i OR OriginalFileName = NOCASE("\REGSVR32.EXE")) AND CommandLine ICONTAINS " \\"

rules.name: Potentially Suspicious Regsvr32 HTTP/FTP Pattern
rules.splunk: Image="*\\regsvr32.exe" OR OriginalFileName="REGSVR32.EXE" CommandLine IN ("* /i*", "* -i*") CommandLine IN ("*ftp*", "*http*")

rules.insightidr: (Image=/.*\\regsvr32\.exe$/i OR OriginalFileName = NOCASE("REGSVR32.EXE")) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [" /i", " -i"]) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["ftp", "http"])

rules.name: Potentially Suspicious Regsvr32 HTTP IP Pattern
rules.insightidr: (Image=/.*\\regsvr32\.exe$/i OR OriginalFileName = NOCASE("REGSVR32.EXE")) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [" /i:http://1", " /i:http://2", " /i:http://3", " /i:http://4", " /i:http://5", " /i:http://6", " /i:http://7", " /i:http://8", " /i:http://9", " /i:https://1", " /i:https://2", " /i:https://3", " /i:https://4", " /i:https://5", " /i:https://6", " /i:https://7", " /i:https://8", " /i:https://9", " -i:http://1", " -i:http://2", " -i:http://3", " -i:http://4", " -i:http://5", " -i:http://6", " -i:http://7", " -i:http://8", " -i:http://9", " -i:https://1", " -i:https://2", " -i:https://3", " -i:https://4", " -i:https://5", " -i:https://6", " -i:https://7", " -i:https://8", " -i:https://9"])

rules.name: Potential Regsvr32 Commandline Flag Anomaly
rules.elastic: (process.executable:*\\regsvr32.exe AND (process.command_line:("*\ \/i\:*" OR "*\ \-i\:*"))) AND (NOT (process.command_line:("*\ \/n\ *" OR "*\ \-n\ *")))
rules.insightidr: Image=/.*\\regsvr32\.exe$/i AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [" /i:", " -i:"]) AND NOT (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [" /n ", " -n "])

rules.name: Persistence Via TypedPaths - CommandLine
rules.elastic: process.command_line:*\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Explorer\\TypedPaths*
rules.insightidr: CommandLine ICONTAINS "\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Explorer\TypedPaths"

rules.name: Potential PowerShell Execution Policy Tampering - ProcCreation
rules.elastic: (process.command_line:(*\\ShellIds\\Microsoft.PowerShell\\ExecutionPolicy* OR *\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows\\PowerShell\\ExecutionPolicy*)) AND (process.command_line:(*Bypass* OR *RemoteSigned* OR *Unrestricted*))
rules.insightidr: (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["\ShellIds\Microsoft.PowerShell\ExecutionPolicy", "\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\PowerShell\ExecutionPolicy"]) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["Bypass", "RemoteSigned", "Unrestricted"])

rules.name: Potential Provisioning Registry Key Abuse For Binary Proxy Execution
rules.elastic: process.command_line:*SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Provisioning\\Commands\\*
rules.insightidr: CommandLine ICONTAINS "SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Provisioning\Commands\"

rules.name: Potential Privilege Escalation via Service Permissions Weakness
rules.elastic: winlog.event_data.IntegrityLevel:Medium AND (process.command_line:*ControlSet* AND process.command_line:*services*) AND (process.command_line:(*\\ImagePath* OR *\\FailureCommand* OR *\\ServiceDll*))
rules.insightidr: IntegrityLevel = NOCASE("Medium") AND CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["ControlSet", "services"] AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["\ImagePath", "\FailureCommand", "\ServiceDll"])

rules.name: Potential Credential Dumping Attempt Using New NetworkProvider - CLI

rules.name: Potential Persistence Via Logon Scripts - CommandLine

rules.name: Exports Critical Registry Keys To a File

rules.name: Detected Windows Software Discovery

rules.insightidr: Image=/.*\\reg\.exe$/i AND CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["query", "\software\", "/v", "svcversion"]

rules.name: Changing Existing Service ImagePath Value Via Reg.EXE
rules.splunk: Image="*\\reg.exe" CommandLine="*add *" CommandLine="*SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\*" CommandLine="* ImagePath *" CommandLine IN ("* /d *", "* -d *")
rules.elastic: (process.executable:*\\reg.exe AND (process.command_line:"*add\ *" AND process.command_line:*SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\* AND process.command_line:"*\ ImagePath\ *")) AND (process.command_line:("*\ \/d\ *" OR "*\ \-d\ *"))
rules.insightidr: Image=/.*\\reg\.exe$/i AND CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["add ", "SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\", " ImagePath "] AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [" /d ", " -d "])

rules.name: Suspicious ScreenSave Change by Reg.exe
rules.splunk: Image="*\\reg.exe" CommandLine IN ("*HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Control Panel\\Desktop*", "*HKCU\\Control Panel\\Desktop*") (CommandLine="*/v ScreenSaveActive*" CommandLine="*/t REG_SZ*" CommandLine="*/d 1*" CommandLine="*/f*") OR (CommandLine="*/v ScreenSaveTimeout*" CommandLine="*/t REG_SZ*" CommandLine="*/d *" CommandLine="*/f*") OR (CommandLine="*/v ScreenSaverIsSecure*" CommandLine="*/t REG_SZ*" CommandLine="*/d 0*" CommandLine="*/f*") OR (CommandLine="*/v SCRNSAVE.EXE*" CommandLine="*/t REG_SZ*" CommandLine="*/d *" CommandLine="*.scr*" CommandLine="*/f*")
rules.elastic: (process.executable:*\\reg.exe AND (process.command_line:("*HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Control\ Panel\\Desktop*" OR "*HKCU\\Control\ Panel\\Desktop*"))) AND ((process.command_line:"*\/v\ ScreenSaveActive*" AND process.command_line:"*\/t\ REG_SZ*" AND process.command_line:"*\/d\ 1*" AND process.command_line:*\/f*) OR (process.command_line:"*\/v\ ScreenSaveTimeout*" AND process.command_line:"*\/t\ REG_SZ*" AND process.command_line:"*\/d\ *" AND process.command_line:*\/f*) OR (process.command_line:"*\/v\ ScreenSaverIsSecure*" AND process.command_line:"*\/t\ REG_SZ*" AND process.command_line:"*\/d\ 0*" AND process.command_line:*\/f*) OR (process.command_line:"*\/v\ SCRNSAVE.EXE*" AND process.command_line:"*\/t\ REG_SZ*" AND process.command_line:"*\/d\ *" AND process.command_line:*.scr* AND process.command_line:*\/f*))
rules.insightidr: Image=/.*\\reg\.exe$/i AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Control Panel\Desktop", "HKCU\Control Panel\Desktop"]) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["/v ScreenSaveActive", "/t REG_SZ", "/d 1", "/f"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["/v ScreenSaveTimeout", "/t REG_SZ", "/d ", "/f"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["/v ScreenSaverIsSecure", "/t REG_SZ", "/d 0", "/f"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["/v SCRNSAVE.EXE", "/t REG_SZ", "/d ", ".scr", "/f"])

rules.name: Python Spawning Pretty TTY on Windows
rules.splunk: Image IN ("*python.exe", "*python3.exe", "*python2.exe") (CommandLine="*import pty*" CommandLine="*.spawn(*") OR CommandLine="*from pty import spawn*"
rules.elastic: (process.executable:(*python.exe OR *python3.exe OR *python2.exe)) AND ((process.command_line:"*import\ pty*" AND process.command_line:*.spawn\(*) OR process.command_line:"*from\ pty\ import\ spawn*")
rules.insightidr: (Image=/(.*python\.exe$|.*python3\.exe$|.*python2\.exe$)/i) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["import pty", ".spawn("] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS "from pty import spawn")

rules.name: Python Inline Command Execution
rules.splunk: OriginalFileName="python.exe" OR Image IN ("*python.exe", "*python3.exe", "*python2.exe") CommandLine="* -c*" NOT ((ParentImage="C:\\Program Files\\Python*" ParentImage="*\\python.exe" ParentCommandLine="*-E -s -m ensurepip -U --default-pip*") OR ParentImage="*\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Microsoft VS Code\\Code.exe")
rules.elastic: ((process.pe.original_file_name:python.exe OR (process.executable:(*python.exe OR *python3.exe OR *python2.exe))) AND process.command_line:"*\ \-c*") AND (NOT ((process.parent.executable:"C\:\\Program\ Files\\Python*" AND process.parent.executable:*\\python.exe AND process.parent.command_line:"*\-E\ \-s\ \-m\ ensurepip\ \-U\ \-\-default\-pip*") OR process.parent.executable:"*\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Microsoft\ VS\ Code\\Code.exe"))
rules.insightidr: (OriginalFileName = NOCASE("python.exe") OR Image=/(.*python\.exe$|.*python3\.exe$|.*python2\.exe$)/i) AND CommandLine ICONTAINS " -c" AND NOT (ParentImage ISTARTS-WITH "C:\Program Files\Python" AND ParentImage=/.*\\python\.exe$/i AND ParentCommandLine ICONTAINS "-E -s -m ensurepip -U --default-pip" OR ParentImage=/.*\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Microsoft\ VS\ Code\\Code\.exe$/i)

rules.name: PUA - Adidnsdump Execution
rules.elastic: process.executable:*\\python.exe AND process.command_line:*adidnsdump*
rules.insightidr: Image=/.*\\python\.exe$/i AND CommandLine ICONTAINS "adidnsdump"

rules.name: PUA - Wsudo Suspicious Execution
rules.splunk: Image="*\\wsudo.exe" OR OriginalFileName="wsudo.exe" OR Description="Windows sudo utility" OR ParentImage="*\\wsudo-bridge.exe" OR CommandLine IN ("*-u System*", "*-uSystem*", "*-u TrustedInstaller*", "*-uTrustedInstaller*", "* --ti *")
rules.elastic: (process.executable:*\\wsudo.exe OR process.pe.original_file_name:wsudo.exe OR process.pe.description:"Windows\ sudo\ utility" OR process.parent.executable:*\\wsudo\-bridge.exe) OR (process.command_line:("*\-u\ System*" OR *\-uSystem* OR "*\-u\ TrustedInstaller*" OR *\-uTrustedInstaller* OR "*\ \-\-ti\ *"))
rules.insightidr: Image=/.*\\wsudo\.exe$/i OR OriginalFileName = NOCASE("wsudo.exe") OR Description = NOCASE("Windows sudo utility") OR ParentImage=/.*\\wsudo\-bridge\.exe$/i OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["-u System", "-uSystem", "-u TrustedInstaller", "-uTrustedInstaller", " --ti "]

rules.name: PUA - WebBrowserPassView Execution
rules.splunk: Description="Web Browser Password Viewer" OR Image="*\\WebBrowserPassView.exe"
rules.elastic: process.pe.description:"Web\ Browser\ Password\ Viewer" OR process.executable:*\\WebBrowserPassView.exe
rules.insightidr: Description = NOCASE("Web Browser Password Viewer") OR Image=/.*\\WebBrowserPassView\.exe$/i

rules.name: PUA - Rclone Execution
rules.splunk: (CommandLine="*--config *" CommandLine="*--no-check-certificate *" CommandLine="* copy *") OR (Image="*\\rclone.exe" OR Description="Rsync for cloud storage" CommandLine IN ("*pass*", "*user*", "*copy*", "*sync*", "*config*", "*lsd*", "*remote*", "*ls*", "*mega*", "*pcloud*", "*ftp*", "*ignore-existing*", "*auto-confirm*", "*transfers*", "*multi-thread-streams*", "*no-check-certificate *")) | table CommandLine,ParentCommandLine,Details
rules.elastic: (process.command_line:"*\-\-config\ *" AND process.command_line:"*\-\-no\-check\-certificate\ *" AND process.command_line:"*\ copy\ *") OR ((process.executable:*\\rclone.exe OR process.pe.description:"Rsync\ for\ cloud\ storage") AND (process.command_line:(*pass* OR *user* OR *copy* OR *sync* OR *config* OR *lsd* OR *remote* OR *ls* OR *mega* OR *pcloud* OR *ftp* OR *ignore\-existing* OR *auto\-confirm* OR *transfers* OR *multi\-thread\-streams* OR "*no\-check\-certificate\ *")))

rules.insightidr: (Image=/(.*\\rcedit\-x64\.exe$|.*\\rcedit\-x86\.exe$)/i OR Description = NOCASE("Edit resources of exe") OR Product = NOCASE("rcedit")) AND CommandLine ICONTAINS "--set-" AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["OriginalFileName", "CompanyName", "FileDescription", "ProductName", "ProductVersion", "LegalCopyright"])

rules.elastic: (process.executable:(*\\powershell.exe OR *\\pwsh.exe)) AND (process.command_line:*Add\-PSSnapin* AND process.command_line:*Get\-Recipient* AND process.command_line:*\-ExpandProperty* AND process.command_line:*EmailAddresses* AND process.command_line:*SmtpAddress* AND process.command_line:*\-hidetableheaders*)
rules.insightidr: (Image=/(.*\\powershell\.exe$|.*\\pwsh\.exe$)/i) AND CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["Add-PSSnapin", "Get-Recipient", "-ExpandProperty", "EmailAddresses", "SmtpAddress", "-hidetableheaders"]

rules.name: PowerShell Download Pattern
rules.splunk: Image IN ("*\\powershell.exe", "*\\pwsh.exe") OR OriginalFileName IN ("PowerShell.EXE", "pwsh.dll") CommandLine="*new-object*" CommandLine="*net.webclient).*" CommandLine="*download*" CommandLine IN ("*string(*", "*file(*") | table CommandLine,ParentCommandLine
rules.elastic: ((process.executable:(*\\powershell.exe OR *\\pwsh.exe)) OR (process.pe.original_file_name:(PowerShell.EXE OR pwsh.dll))) AND ((process.command_line:*new\-object* AND process.command_line:*net.webclient\).* AND process.command_line:*download*) AND (process.command_line:(*string\(* OR *file\(*)))
rules.insightidr: (Image=/(.*\\powershell\.exe$|.*\\pwsh\.exe$)/i OR OriginalFileName IIN ["PowerShell.EXE", "pwsh.dll"]) AND CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["new-object", "net.webclient).", "download"] AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["string(", "file("])

rules.name: PowerShell Download and Execution Cradles
rules.elastic: (process.command_line:(*.DownloadString\(* OR *.DownloadFile\(* OR "*Invoke\-WebRequest\ *" OR "*iwr\ *")) AND (process.command_line:("*;iex\ $*" OR "*\|\ IEX*" OR "*\|IEX\ *" OR *I`E`X* OR *I`EX* OR *IE`X* OR "*iex\ *" OR "*IEX\ \(*" OR *IEX\(* OR *Invoke\-Expression*))
rules.insightidr: (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [".DownloadString(", ".DownloadFile(", "Invoke-WebRequest ", "iwr "]) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [";iex $", "| IEX", "|IEX ", "I`E`X", "I`EX", "IE`X", "iex ", "IEX (", "IEX(", "Invoke-Expression"])

rules.name: Potential DLL File Download Via PowerShell Invoke-WebRequest
rules.elastic: (process.command_line:("*Invoke\-WebRequest\ *" OR "*IWR\ *")) AND (process.command_line:*http* AND process.command_line:*OutFile* AND process.command_line:*.dll*)
rules.insightidr: (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["Invoke-WebRequest ", "IWR "]) AND CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["http", "OutFile", ".dll"]

rules.name: PowerShell Web Download
rules.elastic: process.command_line:(*.DownloadString\(* OR *.DownloadFile\(* OR "*Invoke\-WebRequest\ *" OR "*iwr\ *")
rules.insightidr: CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [".DownloadString(", ".DownloadFile(", "Invoke-WebRequest ", "iwr "]

rules.name: Potential COM Objects Download Cradles Usage - Process Creation
Potential PowerShell Downgrade Attack
rules.elastic: process.executable:*\\powershell.exe AND (process.command_line:("*\ \-version\ 2\ *" OR "*\ \-versio\ 2\ *" OR "*\ \-versi\ 2\ *" OR "*\ \-vers\ 2\ *" OR "*\ \-ver\ 2\ *" OR "*\ \-ve\ 2\ *" OR "*\ \-v\ 2\ *"))
rules.insightidr: Image=/.*\\powershell\.exe$/i AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [" -version 2 ", " -versio 2 ", " -versi 2 ", " -vers 2 ", " -ver 2 ", " -ve 2 ", " -v 2 "])

rules.name: Potential PowerShell Execution Via DLL
rules.splunk: Image IN ("*\\rundll32.exe", "*\\regsvcs.exe", "*\\InstallUtil.exe", "*\\regasm.exe") OR OriginalFileName IN ("RUNDLL32.EXE", "RegSvcs.exe", "InstallUtil.exe", "RegAsm.exe") CommandLine IN ("*Default.GetString*", "*FromBase64String*", "*Invoke-Expression*", "*IEX *", "*Invoke-Command*", "*ICM *", "*DownloadString*")
rules.elastic: ((process.executable:(*\\rundll32.exe OR *\\regsvcs.exe OR *\\InstallUtil.exe OR *\\regasm.exe)) OR (process.pe.original_file_name:(RUNDLL32.EXE OR RegSvcs.exe OR InstallUtil.exe OR RegAsm.exe))) AND (process.command_line:(*Default.GetString* OR *FromBase64String* OR *Invoke\-Expression* OR "*IEX\ *" OR *Invoke\-Command* OR "*ICM\ *" OR *DownloadString*))
rules.insightidr: (Image=/(.*\\rundll32\.exe$|.*\\regsvcs\.exe$|.*\\InstallUtil\.exe$|.*\\regasm\.exe$)/i OR OriginalFileName IIN ["RUNDLL32.EXE", "RegSvcs.exe", "InstallUtil.exe", "RegAsm.exe"]) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["Default.GetString", "FromBase64String", "Invoke-Expression", "IEX ", "Invoke-Command", "ICM ", "DownloadString"])

rules.name: Disabled IE Security Features
rules.splunk: (CommandLine="* -name IEHarden *" CommandLine="* -value 0 *") OR (CommandLine="* -name DEPOff *" CommandLine="* -value 1 *") OR (CommandLine="* -name DisableFirstRunCustomize *" CommandLine="* -value 2 *")
rules.elastic: (process.command_line:"*\ \-name\ IEHarden\ *" AND process.command_line:"*\ \-value\ 0\ *") OR (process.command_line:"*\ \-name\ DEPOff\ *" AND process.command_line:"*\ \-value\ 1\ *") OR (process.command_line:"*\ \-name\ DisableFirstRunCustomize\ *" AND process.command_line:"*\ \-value\ 2\ *")
rules.insightidr: CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL [" -name IEHarden ", " -value 0 "] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL [" -name DEPOff ", " -value 1 "] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL [" -name DisableFirstRunCustomize ", " -value 2 "]

rules.name: Windows Firewall Disabled via PowerShell
rules.splunk: Image IN ("*\\powershell.exe", "*\\pwsh.exe", "*\\powershell_ise.exe") OR OriginalFileName IN ("PowerShell.EXE", "pwsh.dll") CommandLine="*Set-NetFirewallProfile *" CommandLine="* -Enabled *" CommandLine="* False*" CommandLine IN ("* -All *", "*Public*", "*Domain*", "*Private*")
rules.elastic: ((process.executable:(*\\powershell.exe OR *\\pwsh.exe OR *\\powershell_ise.exe)) OR (process.pe.original_file_name:(PowerShell.EXE OR pwsh.dll))) AND (process.command_line:"*Set\-NetFirewallProfile\ *" AND process.command_line:"*\ \-Enabled\ *" AND process.command_line:"*\ False*") AND (process.command_line:("*\ \-All\ *" OR *Public* OR *Domain* OR *Private*))
rules.insightidr: (Image=/(.*\\powershell\.exe$|.*\\pwsh\.exe$|.*\\powershell_ise\.exe$)/i OR OriginalFileName IIN ["PowerShell.EXE", "pwsh.dll"]) AND CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["Set-NetFirewallProfile ", " -Enabled ", " False"] AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY [" -All ", "Public", "Domain", "Private"])

rules.name: Disable Windows Defender AV Security Monitoring
rules.splunk: (Image IN ("*\\powershell.exe", "*\\pwsh.exe") OR OriginalFileName IN ("PowerShell.EXE", "pwsh.dll") CommandLine IN ("*-DisableBehaviorMonitoring $true*", "*-DisableRuntimeMonitoring $true*")) OR (Image="*\\sc.exe" OR OriginalFileName="sc.exe" (CommandLine="*stop*" CommandLine="*WinDefend*") OR (CommandLine="*delete*" CommandLine="*WinDefend*") OR (CommandLine="*config*" CommandLine="*WinDefend*" CommandLine="*start=disabled*"))
rules.elastic: (((process.executable:(*\\powershell.exe OR *\\pwsh.exe)) OR (process.pe.original_file_name:(PowerShell.EXE OR pwsh.dll))) AND (process.command_line:("*\-DisableBehaviorMonitoring\ $true*" OR "*\-DisableRuntimeMonitoring\ $true*"))) OR ((process.executable:*\\sc.exe OR process.pe.original_file_name:sc.exe) AND ((process.command_line:*stop* AND process.command_line:*WinDefend*) OR (process.command_line:*delete* AND process.command_line:*WinDefend*) OR (process.command_line:*config* AND process.command_line:*WinDefend* AND process.command_line:*start\=disabled*)))
rules.insightidr: (Image=/(.*\\powershell\.exe$|.*\\pwsh\.exe$)/i OR OriginalFileName IIN ["PowerShell.EXE", "pwsh.dll"]) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["-DisableBehaviorMonitoring $true", "-DisableRuntimeMonitoring $true"]) OR (Image=/.*\\sc\.exe$/i OR OriginalFileName = NOCASE("sc.exe")) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["stop", "WinDefend"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["delete", "WinDefend"] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL ["config", "WinDefend", "start=disabled"])

rules.name: Powershell Defender Exclusion
rules.elastic: (process.command_line:("*Add\-MpPreference\ *" OR "*Set\-MpPreference\ *")) AND (process.command_line:("*\ \-ExclusionPath\ *" OR "*\ \-ExclusionExtension\ *" OR "*\ \-ExclusionProcess\ *" OR "*\ \-ExclusionIpAddress\ *"))

rules.name: PowerShell Execution With Potential Decryption Capabilities
rules.splunk: Image IN ("*\\powershell.exe", "*\\pwsh.exe") OriginalFileName IN ("PowerShell.EXE", "pwsh.dll") CommandLine IN ("*Get-ChildItem *", "*dir *", "*gci *", "*ls *") CommandLine IN ("*Get-Content *", "*gc *", "*cat *", "*type *", "*ReadAllBytes*") (CommandLine="* ^| *" CommandLine="*\*.lnk*" CommandLine="*-Recurse*" CommandLine="*-Skip *") OR (CommandLine="* -ExpandProperty *" CommandLine="*\*.lnk*" CommandLine="*WriteAllBytes*" CommandLine="* .length *")
rules.elastic: ((process.executable:(*\\powershell.exe OR *\\pwsh.exe)) AND (process.pe.original_file_name:(PowerShell.EXE OR pwsh.dll))) AND (process.command_line:("*Get\-ChildItem\ *" OR "*dir\ *" OR "*gci\ *" OR "*ls\ *")) AND (process.command_line:("*Get\-Content\ *" OR "*gc\ *" OR "*cat\ *" OR "*type\ *" OR *ReadAllBytes*)) AND ((process.command_line:"*\ \^\|\ *" AND process.command_line:*\*.lnk* AND process.command_line:*\-Recurse* AND process.command_line:"*\-Skip\ *") OR (process.command_line:"*\ \-ExpandProperty\ *" AND process.command_line:*\*.lnk* AND process.command_line:*WriteAllBytes* AND process.command_line:"*\ .length\ *"))
rules.insightidr: (Image=/(.*\\powershell\.exe$|.*\\pwsh\.exe$)/i) AND (OriginalFileName IIN ["PowerShell.EXE", "pwsh.dll"]) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["Get-ChildItem ", "dir ", "gci ", "ls "]) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ANY ["Get-Content ", "gc ", "cat ", "type ", "ReadAllBytes"]) AND (CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL [" ^| ", ".lnk", "-Recurse", "-Skip "] OR CommandLine ICONTAINS-ALL [" -ExpandProperty ", ".lnk", "WriteAllBytes", " .length "])

rules.elastic: dns.question.name:*servicebus.windows.net* AND process.executable:*HybridConnectionManager*
rules.insightidr: QueryName ICONTAINS "servicebus.windows.net" AND Image ICONTAINS "HybridConnectionManager"

rules.name: DNS Server Discovery Via LDAP Query
rules.splunk: QueryName="_ldap.*" NOT (Image IN ("*:\\Program Files\\*", "*:\\Program Files (x86)\\*", "*:\\Windows\\*") OR (Image="*:\\ProgramData\\Microsoft\\Windows Defender\\Platform\\*" Image="*\\MsMpEng.exe") OR Image="<unknown process>" OR Image!=*) NOT (Image="C:\\WindowsAzure\\GuestAgent*" OR Image IN ("*\\chrome.exe", "*\\firefox.exe", "*\\opera.exe"))
rules.elastic: dns.question.name:_ldap.* AND (NOT ((process.executable:("*\:\\Program\ Files\\*" OR "*\:\\Program\ Files\ \(x86\)\\*" OR *\:\\Windows\\*)) OR (process.executable:"*\:\\ProgramData\\Microsoft\\Windows\ Defender\\Platform\\*" AND process.executable:*\\MsMpEng.exe) OR process.executable:"\<unknown\ process\>" OR (NOT _exists_:process.executable))) AND (NOT (process.executable:C\:\\WindowsAzure\\GuestAgent* OR (process.executable:(*\\chrome.exe OR *\\firefox.exe OR *\\opera.exe))))
rules.insightidr: QueryName ISTARTS-WITH "_ldap." AND NOT (Image ICONTAINS-ANY [":\Program Files\", ":\Program Files (x86)\", ":\Windows\"] OR Image ICONTAINS ":\ProgramData\Microsoft\Windows Defender\Platform\" AND Image=/.*\\MsMpEng\.exe$/i OR Image = NOCASE("<unknown process>") OR Image = null) AND NOT (Image ISTARTS-WITH "C:\WindowsAzure\GuestAgent" OR Image=/(.*\\chrome\.exe$|.*\\firefox\.exe$|.*\\opera\.exe$)/i)

rules.name: DNS Query To Devtunnels Domain
rules.elastic: dns.question.name:*.devtunnels.ms
rules.insightidr: QueryName=/.*\.devtunnels\.ms$/i

rules.name: Cloudflared Tunnels Related DNS Requests
rules.elastic: dns.question.name:(*.v2.argotunnel.com OR *protocol\-v2.argotunnel.com OR *trycloudflare.com OR *update.argotunnel.com)
rules.insightidr: QueryName=/(.*\.v2\.argotunnel\.com$|.*protocol\-v2\.argotunnel\.com$|.*trycloudflare\.com$|.*update\.argotunnel\.com$)/i

rules.name: AppX Package Installation Attempts Via AppInstaller.EXE
rules.elastic: process.executable:"C\:\\Program\ Files\\WindowsApps\\Microsoft.DesktopAppInstaller_*" AND process.executable:*\\AppInstaller.exe
rules.insightidr: Image ICONTAINS-ALL ["C:\Program Files\WindowsApps\Microsoft.DesktopAppInstaller_", "\AppInstaller.exe"]

rules.name: DNS Query for Anonfiles.com Domain - Sysmon
rules.elastic: dns.question.name:*.anonfiles.com*
rules.insightidr: QueryName ICONTAINS ".anonfiles.com"

rules.name: Potentially Suspicious File Download From ZIP TLD
rules.elastic: winlog.event_data.Contents:*.zip\/* AND (file.path:(*.bat\:Zone* OR *.dat\:Zone* OR *.dll\:Zone* OR *.doc\:Zone* OR *.docm\:Zone* OR *.exe\:Zone* OR *.hta\:Zone* OR *.pptm\:Zone* OR *.ps1\:Zone* OR *.rar\:Zone* OR *.rtf\:Zone* OR *.sct\:Zone* OR *.vbe\:Zone* OR *.vbs\:Zone* OR *.ws\:Zone* OR *.wsf\:Zone* OR *.xll\:Zone* OR *.xls\:Zone* OR *.xlsm\:Zone* OR *.zip\:Zone*))
rules.insightidr: Contents ICONTAINS ".zip/" AND (TargetFilename ICONTAINS-ANY [".bat:Zone", ".dat:Zone", ".dll:Zone", ".doc:Zone", ".docm:Zone", ".exe:Zone", ".hta:Zone", ".pptm:Zone", ".ps1:Zone", ".rar:Zone", ".rtf:Zone", ".sct:Zone", ".vbe:Zone", ".vbs:Zone", ".ws:Zone", ".wsf:Zone", ".xll:Zone", ".xls:Zone", ".xlsm:Zone", ".zip:Zone"])

rules.name: Potential Suspicious Winget Package Installation
rules.elastic: winlog.event_data.Contents:"\[ZoneTransfer\]\ \ ZoneId\=3*" AND (winlog.event_data.Contents:(*\:\/\/1* OR *\:\/\/2* OR *\:\/\/3* OR *\:\/\/4* OR *\:\/\/5* OR *\:\/\/6* OR *\:\/\/7* OR *\:\/\/8* OR *\:\/\/9*)) AND file.path:*\:Zone.Identifier AND file.path:*\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\WinGet\\*
rules.insightidr: Contents ISTARTS-WITH "[ZoneTransfer]  ZoneId=3" AND (Contents ICONTAINS-ANY ["://1", "://2", "://3", "://4", "://5", "://6", "://7", "://8", "://9"]) AND TargetFilename=/.*:Zone\.Identifier$/i AND TargetFilename ICONTAINS "\AppData\Local\Temp\WinGet\"

rules.name: Unusual File Download from Direct IP Address
rules.elastic: winlog.event_data.Contents:/http[s]?:\/\/[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}/ AND (file.path:(*.ps1\:Zone* OR *.bat\:Zone* OR *.exe\:Zone* OR *.vbe\:Zone* OR *.vbs\:Zone* OR *.dll\:Zone* OR *.one\:Zone* OR *.cmd\:Zone* OR *.hta\:Zone* OR *.xll\:Zone* OR *.lnk\:Zone*))

rules.name: Exports Registry Key To an Alternate Data Stream
rules.elastic: process.executable:*\\regedit.exe
rules.insightidr: Image=/.*\\regedit\.exe$/i
